{"TopicId":190320,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How do I rotate a rocket in the vab on ps4","CreatedByName":"Supergamer","CreatedById":201793,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T05:26:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Supergamer","CreatedById":201793,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T05:26:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI built my rocket in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003Esph\u003C/abbr\u003E and I saved it. I went to the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003Evab\u003C/abbr\u003E and I found out I needed to rotate the rocket so I can launch. I don\u0027t know how to rotate it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T05:31:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, and welcome to the forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201793-supergamer/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022201793\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201793-supergamer/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Supergamer\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve moved your question over to our Gameplay Questions subforums as the answer should be the same as on PC, and it\u0027s not a technical issue with the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"micha","CreatedById":113840,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T08:07:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the root node (usually the command capsule), then either use the rotate widget or the rotate key commands (use SHIFT to rotate smaller increments than 90deg).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: PS. Pressing \u0026lt;space\u0026gt; while rotating will reset the orientation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-12-12T08:08:23Z\u0022 title=\u002212/12/2019 08:08  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 12, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by micha\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T10:53:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223716423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022190320\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221576138025\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113840\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022micha\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, micha said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelect the root node (usually the command capsule),\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor shift-click on any part if the root part is hard to get.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drpunk","CreatedById":200335,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T11:25:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn PS4 the dpad does rotation of selected part. Left/right, up/down, L1\u002Bleft/L1\u002Bright rotate on the 3 axis.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHalf the fun is seeing if you can guess which buttons you need to use to rotate in the direction you want before exhausting all possibilities. Chances are you won\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-12-12T11:50:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223716464\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022190320\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221576149940\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200335\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022drpunk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, drpunk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHalf the fun is seeing if you can guess which buttons you need to use to rotate in the direction you want before exhausting all possibilities. Chances are you won\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, that\u0027s not too different from the PC version then. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}